Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
com.example.studiomanagergui.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
The FitnessClass class represents a fitness class with information such as class details, instructor, location, time, and lists of members and guests attending the class.
Author:
Priyansh Parikh, Siddarth Seloth
